            <section>
                <h3>.live()</h3>
                <h4>Born: 1.3 Deprecated: 1.7 Removed: 1.9</h4>
                <pre><code class="javascript">//Using live
$('selector').live('click', callback);
//Behind the scenes
$('body').on('click', 'selector', callback);</code></pre>
                <div>
                    <p class="fragment">
                        .live() attaches a click event to the body element.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fragment">
                        An event is fired when ANY element is clicked inside the body tag.
                    </p>
                    <p class="fragment">
                        The event continues if the clicked event matches the selector.
                    </p>
                </div>
